author: Anne Lucey, Barry Roche, Stephen Maguire
title: Coronavirus: Getaway hopefuls told Kerry holiday homes out of bounds
description: Checkpoints pledged by gardaí countrywide in attempt to contain spread of contagion
content:
Some holiday homeowners in Kerry last weekend found gardaí at their door, inquiring where they were from and offering gentle encouragement to go back there.
